'''2016年[[聖多美和普林西比|聖多美和普林西比]]總統選舉'''在2016年7月17日舉行<ref>[https://www.ndi.org/electionscalendar Global elections calendar] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ndi.org/electionscalendar |date=20151022232515 }} NDI</ref>。初步結果顯示{{le|獨立民主行動|Independent Democratic Action}}的[[埃瓦里斯托·卡瓦略|埃瓦里斯托·卡瓦略]]在首輪投票中擊敗現任無黨籍總統[[曼努埃尔·平托·达科斯塔|曼努埃尔·平托·达科斯塔]]當選<ref>[http://www.cmjornal.xl.pt/cm_ao_minuto/detalhe/sao_tomeeleicoes_evaristo_carvalho_eleito_presidente_a_primeira_volta.html São Tomé/Eleições: Evaristo Carvalho eleito Presidente à primeira volta] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cmjornal.xl.pt/cm_ao_minuto/detalhe/sao_tomeeleicoes_evaristo_carvalho_eleito_presidente_a_primeira_volta.html |date=20160719141936 }} Correio de manhã, 18 July 2016</ref>。然而結果隨後被取消，卡瓦略和達科斯塔需進入8月7日舉行的第二輪投票<ref>[http://www.africanews.com/2016/07/22/sao-tome-presidential-election-results-canceled-for-a-second-round/ "Sao Tome presidential election results canceled for a second round"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.africanews.com/2016/07/22/sao-tome-presidential-election-results-canceled-for-a-second-round/ |date=20160724093235 }}, Africanews, 22 July 2016.</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://townhall.com/news/politics-elections/2016/07/24/sao-tome-election-goes-to-second-round-after-court-ruling-n2197202|title=Reuters News - Sao Tome election goes to second round after court ruling|last=News|first=Reuters|website=Townhall|access-date=2016-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725142722/http://townhall.com/news/politics-elections/2016/07/24/sao-tome-election-goes-to-second-round-after-court-ruling-n2197202|archive-date=2016-07-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。然而，平托·達科斯塔聲稱第一輪選舉舞弊後抵制第二輪投票，令卡瓦略自動當選<ref>[http://cen.st/index.php/publicacoes/noticias/item/212-resultados-geral-das-eleicoes-presidenciais-2016 Resultado Geral Provisórios das Eleições Presidenciais 2016 2ª Volta] {{Wayback|url=http://cen.st/index.php/publicacoes/noticias/item/212-resultados-geral-das-eleicoes-presidenciais-2016 |date=20190518214114 }} CEN</ref>。

==選舉制度==
[[聖多美和普林西比民主共和國總統|聖多美和普林西比總統]]採用[[两轮选举制|两轮选举制]]<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2196/ Democratic Republic of Sao Tome and Principe] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2196/ |date=20160729153714 }} IFES</ref>，如果沒有候選人取得50%以上的選票，最高得票的兩名候選人會在8月7日進入次輪選舉。

==候選人==
是次選舉有五名候選人，包括時任總統[[曼努埃尔·平托·达科斯塔|曼努埃尔·平托·达科斯塔]]<ref>[http://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2016/07/15/des-elections-pour-l-archipel-africain-sao-tome-et-principe_4970305_3212.html Des élections pour l’archipel africain Sao Tomé et Principe] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2016/07/15/des-elections-pour-l-archipel-africain-sao-tome-et-principe_4970305_3212.html |date=20160716131240 }} Le Monde, 15 July 2016</ref>、兩位前總理[[埃瓦里斯托·卡瓦略|埃瓦里斯托·卡瓦略]]（{{le|獨立民主行動|Independent Democratic Action}}）和{{le|瑪利亞·達斯內維斯|Maria das Neves}}（{{le|圣多美和普林西比解放运动—社会民主党|Movement for the Liberation of São Tomé and Príncipe/Social Democratic Party|MLSTP/PSD}}）與兩名[[無黨籍|無黨籍]]候選人。

